  "page": "Feature quote/194",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Who in seven hells is this one?” —<a href=\"/index.php/Queen_o%27_whores\" title=\"Queen o&#39; whores\">Prostitute</a><br />“The Lord Commander of the Kingsguard. I might ask the same of you, my lady.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a><br />“Lady? I'm no lady. I'm the queen.” —Prostitute<br />“<a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">My sister</a> will be surprised to hear that.” —Jaime Lannister<br />“Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryman_Frey\" title=\"Ryman Frey\">Ryman</a> crowned me his very self. I'm the queen o' <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">whores</a>.” —Prostitute<br /><i>No, my sweet sister holds that title too.</i> —Jaime Lannister<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, Jaime VI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403110923\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 84/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 303/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/5000000 byt